data.description: Adorable, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath fully remodeled home located near Downtown Hondo with approximately 2185 sq ft.  Situated on a corner lot, blocks away from the courthouse, this home could easily be someone's home or an office. This long-time family home has only had two previous owner's and went through a major renovation in 2021/2022. All new electrical, insulation, sheetrock, drywall, paint, baseboards, interior and exterior doors, granite countertops, plumbing fixtures, lighting fixtures, sprinkler system, etc, etc.  A full list of the upgrades will be available in additional info. All finishes and materials were handpicked and sourced by the current owners, including the copper sink and cabinet pulls, custom 1/2 bath vanity and designer tile. With all the new, a few of the unique features to the house remain like the custom huge stone fireplace in the living room as well as the beautiful refinished, natural hardwood floors.  Two spacious bedrooms are located off of the living room, both with walk-in closets with custom shelving. Off the primary bedroom is a newly tiled master bath with granite countertops, walk in shower and new fixtures.  The hall bath that separates the two bedrooms has new cabinets, countertops, tubs, custom tile, etc.  Looking for storage?  This house has a ton with 4 extra closets outside of the bedrooms along with built-in shelving and lots of cabinet space. The third bedroom can be used as a bedroom or a secondary living area... it's that big.  With new carpet(2023), ceiling fan, recessed lighting and outside access, this is the perfect space for all of your activities.  This house is truly a remarkable find in Hondo.... come take a look today.
